OL,9,G0140FCanals: The Making of a Nation
OL,10,     GLiz McIvor recounts the story of
OL,11,     G'canal mania', the period of
OL,12,     Gactivity that helped develop
OL,13,     GBritain's modern financial
OL,14,     Geconomy, now centred in London.
